Planning biomass calculation


The fifth attachment has "Biomasse im Beet", with volumes from r1, r2, h1, h2, etc.
It includes "Biomasse im oberirdischen Aufwuchs", summing BA(Tree) + AH(Kräuter, Stauden) - BA(FORREST FUELS).
BA(FORREST FUELS) is harvested parts like fruits, leaves, so it's subtracted for net storage.
I'm thinking this model accounts for cumulative biomass over years, which fits COP30 needs.


