Let R be the annual revenue: 9,526,500 EUR
Let G be the carbon credit grant: 500,000 EUR per year
For year t (from 1 to 20):
Outstanding principal at the start of year t: P - (t - 1) * A
Interest payment in year t: r * [P - (t - 1) * A]
SBLC fees in year t: S * [P - (t - 1) * A]
Total outflows in year t: Interest + Principal repayment + SBLC fees + Operational costs
= r * [P - (t - 1) * A] + A + S * [P - (t - 1) * A] + O
Total inflows in year t: R + G
Net cash flow in year t: (R + G) - [r * (P - (t - 1) * A) + A + S * (P - (t - 1) * A) + O]
